Jessica Laura Sutton (a mụrụ na June 2, 1993) bụ onye na-eme ihe nkiri na South Africa
Ọ pụtara na ihe nkiri Netflix The Kissing Booth na dịka onye isi Tally Craven na usoro Freeform Motherland: Fort Salem

A mụrụ Sutton na Cape Town, South Africa. Ọ gara ACT Film Academy ma nata diplọma ya n'afọ 2014 na Advanced Acting for Film ma gaa n'ihu na ọmụmụ ya na Matthew Harrison na The Actors Foundry na Vancouver.

Kemgbe ọ malitere na ihuenyo n'afọ 2015, Jessica apụtala n'ọtụtụ ihe ngosi telivishọn, gụnyere Saints & Strangers, Ice, American Monster na Motherland: Fort Salem Ihe nkiri ya kachasị ọhụrụ, Rogue, bụ Megan Fox ma wepụta ya n'afọ 2020. Ọ pụtakwara na ihe nkiri Detour, Finders Keepers, Bhai's Cafe, Escape Room, The Kissing Booth na Inside Man: Most Wanted
